    <p>After years of duct-taping together scheduling apps, CRM tools, payment platforms, lead trackers, email services, SMS tools, and spreadsheets \'97 the frustration boiled over. None of these tools talked to each other. None of them understood the full picture. None of them generated a single lead. So we built the platform we always needed \'97 and we made it exclusive.</p>\
